jClustering

jClustering is a clustering framework developed for ImageJ.

See:
          Description

Packages
jclustering  
jclustering.metrics  
jclustering.techniques  

 

jClustering is a clustering framework developed for ImageJ. It aims at providing an easy to extend platform in which to develop new clustering algorithms. You can find a comprehensive manual for this plugin on its main page at github, including documentation for developers.
